You will find here all documents which give you an overview of how SMART works. Its not complete but it should be possible to understand SMART's outline. Please use the [http://forum.open-publisher.net/ forum] for further questions.

Take a look at the following diagram. It shows you SMART's main design. In SMART there is a separation of the business and the presentation logic. Or in other words; Data storage, accessing data, data presentation is done in clearly separated sections. Bad application designs mix those sections with no clear plan, which leads into code that is difficult to maintain with growing complexity. 

